about hacking the flow state.

00:00:43.550 --> 00:00:46.390
You are also
creating a flow Dojo,

00:00:46.390 --> 00:00:49.200
which is helping people reverse
engineer their flow states,

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:53.200
and create these ecstatic states
of mind in which people perform

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:55.380
their best and feel their best.

00:00:55.380 --> 00:00:57.740
So tell us about some of
these tools and techniques

00:00:57.740 --> 00:01:01.400
that you're implementing in the
flow Dojo with Steven Kotler.

00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:02.790
What are you guys doing?

00:01:02.790 --> 00:01:05.319
JAMIE WHEAL: Sure, well,
what we're teeing up

00:01:05.319 --> 00:01:08.520
is the world's first
research and training

00:01:08.520 --> 00:01:11.645
facility dedicated to
ultimate human performance,

00:01:11.645 --> 00:01:13.510
or flow states.

00:01:13.510 --> 00:01:15.610
And the premise is
what would happen

00:01:15.610 --> 00:01:19.230
if we took the hands-on science
museum like the Exploratorium

00:01:19.230 --> 00:01:22.420
here in San Francisco, with all
the sort of kinetic exhibits

00:01:22.420 --> 00:01:26.090
the kids get to monkey with
and learn about bigger forces,

00:01:26.090 --> 00:01:29.120
and apply it to,
basically, kinetics--

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:31.980
our bodies-- and
sort of this notion

00:01:31.980 --> 00:01:34.680
that as we train our bodies
and brains to work really well

00:01:34.680 --> 00:01:38.760
together, then our
waking cells get

00:01:38.760 --> 00:01:43.360
to experience more accurate
information processing, greater

00:01:43.360 --> 00:01:45.880
resourcefulness and
emotional resilience,

00:01:45.880 --> 00:01:49.880
and generally amplify pattern
recognition, perspective

00:01:49.880 --> 00:01:53.270
holding, and, therefore, more
increasingly sophisticated

00:01:53.270 --> 00:01:54.690
and accurate decision making.

00:01:54.690 --> 00:01:56.320
JASON SILVA: Flow states--
you feel your best

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:57.403
and you perform your best.

00:01:57.403 --> 00:02:00.570
Elite athletes when they're in
the zone, jazz musicians when

00:02:00.570 --> 00:02:03.870
