00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:19.860
in technology,
psychology, neurobiology,

00:02:19.860 --> 00:02:23.440
and pharmacology--
drugs, right-- we now

00:02:23.440 --> 00:02:29.260
have the capacity to back-door
access these flow states,

00:02:29.260 --> 00:02:32.770
so that they're not haphazard,
fleeting, ephemeral states,

00:02:32.770 --> 00:02:34.770
bu that they become part
of the human experience

00:02:34.770 --> 00:02:35.674
on a daily basis.

00:02:35.674 --> 00:02:36.840
JAMIE WHEAL: Yeah, for sure.

